\n* [[Roma in Romania|Roma]] 0.4%\n\nA 2017 estimate placed the population at 169,316, a 14.98 percent increase since 2011. This increase brings Sibiu's population close to the numbers observed in 1992 when the highest population was recorded.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.turnulsfatului.ro/2017/10/01/statistica-sase-ani-sibiul-crescut-cu-aproape-70-000-de-locuitori/|title=Statistic\u0103: \u00een \u0219ase ani Sibiul a crescut cu aproape 70.000 de locuitori {{!}} Turnul Sfatului Online|date=2017-10-01|work=Turnul Sfatului Online|access-date=2017-10-08|language=ro-RO|url-status=live|archiveurl=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20150526045111/http://www.turnulsfatului.ro/2017/10/01/statistica-sase-ani-sibiul-crescut-cu-aproape-70-000-de-locuitori/|archivedate=2015-05-26}}</ref>\n\n===Population dynamics===\n\n{|class=\"toccolours\" style=\"margin: 0 1em 0 1em;\" width=\"50%\"\n|-\n! align=\"center\" style=\"background:#ccccff\" colspan=3 | Census<ref>{{cite web|url=http://varga.adatbank.transindex.ro/?pg=3&action=etnik&id=6764|title=Erd\u00e9ly etnikai \u00e9s felekezeti statisztik\u00e1ja|website=varga.adatbank.transindex.ro|accessdate=28 April 2018|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071022135715/http://varga.adatbank.transindex.ro/?pg=3&action=etnik&id=6764|archivedate=22 October 2007}}</ref>\n! align=\"center\" style=\"background:#ccccff\" colspan=3 | Ethnic structure\n|-\n|'''Year'''\n|'''Population'''\n|'''%\u00b1'''\n|[[Romanians]]\n|[[Hungarians]]\n|[[Ethnic German|Germans]]\n|----\n|1850\n|12,765\n|\u2014 \n|2,089 \n|977 \n|8,790\n|----\n|1880\n|19,446 \n| + 41.4%\n|2,810 \n|2,065 \n|14,327\n|----\n|1890\n|21,465\n| + 9.8%\n|4,581 \n|3,199 \n|13,148\n|----\n|1900\n|29,577 \n| + 31.7%\n|7,106 \n|5,747 \n|16,141\n|----\n|1910\n|33,489 \n| + 12.4%\n|8,824 \n|7,252 \n|16,832\n|----\n|1920\n|32,748 \n| \u2013 2.2%\n|8,553 \n|4,291 \n|18,218\n|----\n|1930\n|49,345 \n| + 40.4%\n|19,006 \n|6,782 \n|22,045\n|----\n|1941\n|63,765 \n| + 25.5%\n|33,